.rule_6_12_4_ensure_local_logging_is_set_for_authentication_and_authorization_events

Reference: Agency (NSA)
tion-statement/file-edit-accounting-options.html

Remediation: To configure a local SYSLOG file for Auth events, issue the following command from the
[edit system syslog] hierarchy;
[edit system syslog]
user@host#set file <filename> authorization any

.